    -e NO_PROXY="localhost,127.0.0.1" \\
    --restart=unless-stopped -p 8080:8080 rancher/server
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`如果您不使用`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/docs/rancher1/configurations/catalog/_index"
